title: The U.S. Attorney-General Jeff Seaters was dropped for misconduct?
subtitle: The false allegation that Attorney General Jeff Stills would be removed from the Bar Association was published by a letter of complaint signed by 2,000 American lawyers.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The U.S. Attorney-General Jeff Sails will be removed from the Alabama State Bar for a letter of complaint from 2,000 lawyers from all over the United States.
